room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by Red Door Escapes in Little Rock
room_description: Red Door Escapes’ second escape room brings you riddles, writing, and arithmetic (mainly riddles, not so much of the other stuff)! You and your friends must help little Tommy Troublemaker avoid punishment by one of the strictest disciplinarians to ever wield a paddle, Principal Percival Peabody. You will have 60 minutes to get into the Principal’s Office, decipher clues and solve puzzles to erase Tommy’s name from Peabody’s patented “paddle-pointments” program, and escape undetected!
